section.section:
The declaration of intent shall be filed as follows:
in a year in which the Governor is elected, by the date and time specified for a candidate to file a certificate of candidacy;
in the year in which the President and Mayor of Baltimore City are elected, by July 1; and
for a special election to fill a vacancy:
for Representative in Congress, by the date and time specified in the Governor's proclamation for a candidate to file a certificate of candidacy; or
for a local public office, by the date and time specified in the county proclamation for a candidate to file a certificate of candidacy.
